Implementation Plan
•	Environment Setup: Have a localhost (XAMPP) for development and version control repository setup (e.g., GitHub).

•	Database Setup: Created the database and tables using SQL scripts.

•	Frontend: Design and code the HTML pages, style them with CSS and make it interactive using JavaScript.

•	Backend Development: Develop user registration, pet registration and get pet data PHP scripts.

•	Integrating: Link the fields of the frontend form with backend php scripts to save and fetch data from database.

•	Tests: Do as many tests and triages to check that the system works well.

•	Deployment: Place the system in web server and test with real-time environment.
